requests.postData:
{"operationName":"getAccount","variables":{"id":""},"query":"query getAccount($id: ID!) {
  account(id: $id) {
    ...Account
    __typename
  }
}

fragment Account on Account {
  depositedMPL
  id
  isPoolDelegate
  isValidBorrower
  managedPoolsV2 {
    id
    __typename
  }
  totalClaimableFees
  totalClaimableInterest
  totalClaimableReward
  totalClaimableStakeReward
  totalFeesEarned
  totalInterestEarned
  totalPoolTokenBalance
  totalPoolTokensStaked
  totalRewardPaid
  totalStake
  totalStakeLockerTokensStaked
  totalStakeRewardPaid
  withdrawnMPL
  xMPLBalance
  principalOwed
  __typename
}"}

{"operationName":"getAccount","variables":{"id":"0x7e4abd63a7c8314cc28d388303472353d884f292"},"query":"query getAccount($id: ID!) {
  account(id: $id) {
    ...Account
    __typename
  }
}

fragment Account on Account {
  depositedMPL
  id
  isPoolDelegate
  isValidBorrower
  managedPoolsV2 {
    id
    __typename
  }
  totalClaimableFees
  totalClaimableInterest
  totalClaimableReward
  totalClaimableStakeReward
  totalFeesEarned
  totalInterestEarned
  totalPoolTokenBalance
  totalPoolTokensStaked
  totalRewardPaid
  totalStake
  totalStakeLockerTokensStaked
  totalStakeRewardPaid
  withdrawnMPL
  xMPLBalance
  principalOwed
  __typename
}"}

requests.postData:
{"operationName":"getAccount","variables":{"id":""},"query":"query getAccount($id: ID!) {
  account(id: $id) {
    ...Account
    __typename
  }
}

fragment Account on Account {
  depositedMPL
  id
  isPoolDelegate
  isValidBorrower
  managedPoolsV2 {
    id
    __typename
  }
  totalClaimableFees
  totalClaimableInterest
  totalClaimableReward
  totalClaimableStakeReward
  totalFeesEarned
  totalInterestEarned
  totalPoolTokenBalance
  totalPoolTokensStaked
  totalRewardPaid
  totalStake
  totalStakeLockerTokensStaked
  totalStakeRewardPaid
  withdrawnMPL
  xMPLBalance
  principalOwed
  __typename
}"}
